""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[Label], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Version], [t1].[Id], [t1].[ActionName], [t1].[ControllerName], [t1].[ControllerNamespace], [t1].[DisplayName], [t1].[IconClass], [t1].[IconImage], [t1].[IsDefault], [t1].[ModuleId], [t1].[ModuleViewTypeId], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[ControlType], [t1].[ModuleViewId], [t1].[PropertyId], [t1].[Id1], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[DefaultValue], [t1].[Description], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Label], [t1].[LastModifiedDate], [t1].[Name], [t1].[OptionListId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[Id], [d].[CreatedDate], [d].[Description], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Label], [d].[LastModifiedDate], [d].[Name], [d].[Version]
    FROM [dp_Module] AS [d]

    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[ActionName], [d0].[ControllerName], [d0].[ControllerNamespace], [d0].[DisplayName], [d0].[IconClass], [d0].[IconImage], [d0].[IsDefault], [d0].[ModuleId], [d0].[ModuleViewTypeId], [d1].[Id] AS [Id0], [d1].[ControlType], [t0].[ModuleViewId], [t0].[PropertyId], [t0].[Id] AS [Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[DefaultValue], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[Label], [t0].[LastModifiedDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[OptionListId]

        SELECT [d2].[ModuleViewId], [d2].[PropertyId], [d3].[Id], [d3].[CreatedDate], [d3].[DefaultValue], [d3].[Description], [d3].[IsActive], [d3].[Label], [d3].[LastModifiedDate], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OptionListId]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ModuleId]

    SELECT 1
    FROM [dp_UserRole] AS [d1]
    WHERE ([d].[Id] = [d1].[RoleId]) AND ([d1].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0))

    SELECT [d14].[Id], [d14].[ContainerId], [d14].[InheritEditPermissions], [d14].[InheritViewPermissions], [d14].[IsActive], [d14].[ModuleId], [d14].[ModuleViewId], [d14].[PageId], [d14].[Properties], [d14].[SortOrder], [d14].[Title], [d15].[Id] AS [Id0], [d15].[ActionName], [d15].[ControllerName], [d15].[ControllerNamespace], [d15].[DisplayName], [d15].[IconClass], [d15].[IconImage], [d15].[IsDefault], [d15].[ModuleId] AS [ModuleId0], [d15].[ModuleViewTypeId], [t2].[ModuleViewId] AS [ModuleViewId0], [t2].[PropertyId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id1], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[DefaultValue], [t2].[Description], [t2].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [t2].[Label], [t2].[LastModifiedDate], [t2].[Name], [t2].[OptionListId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[IsActive0] AS [IsActive00], [t2].[Label0], [t2].[LastModifiedDate0], [t2].[List], [t2].[Name0], [d19].[Id] AS [Id2], [d19].[PageModuleId], [d19].[PermissionId], [d19].[RoleId]
    FROM [dp_PageModule] AS [d14]
    INNER JOIN [dp_ModuleView] AS [d15] ON [d14].[ModuleViewId] = [d15].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d16].[ModuleViewId], [d16].[PropertyId], [d17].[Id], [d17].[CreatedDate], [d17].[DefaultValue], [d17].[Description], [d17].[IsActive], [d17].[Label], [d17].[LastModifiedDate], [d17].[Name], [d17].[OptionListId], [d18].[Id] AS [Id0], [d18].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d18].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [d18].[Label] AS [Label0], [d18].[LastModifiedDate] AS [LastModifiedDate0], [d18].[List], [d18].[Name] AS [Name0]
        FROM [dp_ModuleViewProperty] AS [d16]
        INNER JOIN [dp_Property] AS [d17] ON [d16].[PropertyId] = [d17].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [dp_OptionList] AS [d18] ON [d17].[OptionListId] = [d18].[Id]
    ) AS [t2] ON [d15].[Id] = [t2].[ModuleViewId]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_ModulePermission] AS [d19] ON [d14].[Id] = [d19].[PageModuleId]
) AS [t3] ON [t].[Id] = [t3].[PageId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[PageId], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [d4].[PageId], [d4].[Locale], [d5].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [t1].[Id2], [t1].[ContentTypeId1], [t1].[PropertyId], [t1].[Id3], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id4], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[ModuleViewId0], [t3].[PropertyId], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id00], [t3].[Id2]"

[t3].[PermissionId], [t3].[RoleId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[Id], [d].[CreatedDate], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[IsIncludedInMenu], [d].[IsSystem], [d].[LastModifiedDate], [d].[LayoutId], [d].[PageLevel], [d].[PageOrder], [d].[PageTypeId], [d].[ParentId], [d].[SiteMapPriority], [d].[StartDate], [d].[ThemeSrc], [d0].[Id] AS [Id0], [d0].[Name], [d1].[PageId], [d1].[ModelName], [d1].[ModuleId], [d2].[Id] AS [Id1], [d2].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d2].[Description], [d2].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [d2].[Label], [d2].[LastModifiedDate] AS [LastModifiedDate0], [d2].[Name] AS [Name0], [d2].[Version], [d3].[Id] AS [Id2], [d3].[Config], [d3].[IsActive] AS [IsActive1], [d3].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [dp_Page] AS [d]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_PageType] AS [d0] ON [d].[PageTypeId] = [d0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_AdminPage] AS [d1] ON [d].[Id] = [d1].[PageId]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_Module] AS [d2] ON [d1].[ModuleId] = [d2].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_Layout] AS [d3] ON [d].[LayoutId] = [d3].[Id]
    WHERE [d].[Id] = @__pageId_0
    ORDER BY [d].[Id]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [dp_PageTranslation] AS [d4] ON [t].[Id] = [d4].[PageId]
LEFT JOIN [dp_PagePermission] AS [d5] ON [t].[Id] = [d5].[PageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[Id], [d6].[ContainerId], [d6].[ContentTypeId], [d6].[CreatedDate], [d6].[InheritEditPermissions], [d6].[InheritViewPermissions], [d6].[IsActive], [d6].[LastModifiedDate], [d6].[PageId], [d6].[Properties], [d6].[SortOrder], [d6].[Title], [d7].[Id] AS [Id0], [d7].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d7].[IconClass], [d7].[IconImage], [d7].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [d7].[IsList], [d7].[Label], [d7].[LastModifiedDate] AS [LastModifiedDate0], [d7].[Name], [d7].[SortOrder] AS [SortOrder0], [d8].[Id] AS [Id1], [d8].[ContentData], [d8].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [d8].[CultureCode], [d8].[IsActive] AS [IsActive1], [d8].[LastModifiedDate] AS [LastModifiedDate1], [d8].[PageContentId], [d9].[Id] AS [Id2], [d9].[ContentFieldTypeId], [d9].[ContentTypeId] AS [ContentTypeId0], [d9].[FieldDescription], [d9].[FieldLabel], [d9].[FieldName], [d9].[IsShownOnList], [d9].[IsShownOnPreview], [d9].[SortOrder] AS [SortOrder1], [t0].[ContentTypeId] AS [ContentTypeId1], [t0].[PropertyId], [t0].[Id] AS [Id3], [t0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [t0].[DefaultValue], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsActive] AS [IsActive2], [t0].[Label] AS [Label0], [t0].[LastModifiedDate] AS [LastModifiedDate2], [t0].[Name] AS [Name0], [t0].[OptionListId], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t0].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t0].[IsActive0] AS [IsActive00], [t0].[Label0] AS [Label00], [t0].[LastModifiedDate0] AS [LastModifiedDate00], [t0].[List], [t0].[Name0] AS [Name00], [d13].[Id] AS [Id4], [d13].[PageContentId] AS [PageContentId0], [d13].[PermissionId], [d13].[RoleId]
    FROM [dp_PageContent] AS [d6]
    INNER JOIN [dp_ContentType] AS [d7] ON [d6].[ContentTypeId] = [d7].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_PageContentTranslation] AS [d8] ON [d6].[Id] = [d8].[PageContentId]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_ContentTypeField] AS [d9] ON [d7].[Id] = [d9].[ContentTypeId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d10].[ContentTypeId], [d10].[PropertyId], [d11].[Id], [d11].[CreatedDate], [d11].[DefaultValue], [d11].[Description], [d11].[IsActive], [d11].[Label], [d11].[LastModifiedDate], [d11].[Name], [d11].[OptionListId], [d12].[Id] AS [Id0], [d12].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d12].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [d12].[Label] AS [Label0], [d12].[LastModifiedDate] AS [LastModifiedDate0], [d12].[List], [d12].[Name] AS [Name0]
        FROM [dp_ContentTypeProperty] AS [d10]
        INNER JOIN [dp_Property] AS [d11] ON [d10].[PropertyId] = [d11].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [dp_OptionList] AS [d12] ON [d11].[OptionListId] = [d12].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [d7].[Id] = [t0].[ContentTypeId]
    LEFT JOIN [dp_ContentPermission] AS [d13] ON [d6].[Id] = [d13].[PageContentId]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[PageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d14].[Id], [d14].[ContainerId], [d14].[InheritEditPermissions], [d14].[InheritViewPermissions], [d14].[IsActive], [d14].[ModuleId], [d14].[ModuleViewId], [d14].[PageId], [d14].[Properties], [d14].[SortOrder], [d14].[Title], [d15].[Id] AS [Id0], [d15].[ActionName], [d15].[ControllerName], [d15].[ControllerNamespace], [d15].[DisplayName], [d15].[IconClass], [d15].[IconImage], [d15].[IsDefault], [d15].[ModuleId] AS [ModuleId0], [d15].[ModuleViewTypeId], [t2].[ModuleViewId] AS [ModuleViewId0], [t2].[PropertyId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id1], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[DefaultValue], [t2].[Description], [t2].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [t2].[Label], [t2].[LastModifiedDate], [t2].[Name], [t2].[OptionListId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[IsActive0] AS [IsActive00], [t2].[Label0], [t2].[LastModifiedDate0], [t2].[List], [t2].[Name0], [d19].[Id] AS [Id2], [d19].[PageModuleId], [d19].[PermissionId], [d19].[RoleId]

) AS [t3] ON [t].[Id] = [t3].[PageId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[PageId], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [d4].[PageId], [d4].[Locale], [d5].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [t1].[Id2], [t1].[ContentTypeId1], [t1].[PropertyId], [t1].[Id3], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id4], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[ModuleViewId0], [t3].[PropertyId], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id00], [t3].[Id2]"
